geomancy.effects: Takes one turn to charge, then raises the user's Special Attack, Special Defense, and Speed by two stages.
geomancy.name: Geomancy

magneticflux.effects: Raises the Defense and Special Defense of all friendly Pokémon with plus or minus by one stage.
magneticflux.name: Magnetic Flux

electricterrain.effects: For five turns, prevents all Pokémon on the ground from sleeping and strengthens their electric moves to 1.5× their power.
electricterrain.name: Electric Terrain

dazzlinggleam.effects: Inflicts regular damage with no additional effect.
dazzlinggleam.name: Dazzling Gleam

babydolleyes.effects: Lowers the target's Attack by one stage.
babydolleyes.name: Baby-Doll Eyes

nuzzle.effects: Has a 100% chance to paralyze the target.
nuzzle.name: Nuzzle

holdback.effects: Cannot lower the target's HP below 1.
holdback.name: Hold Back

infestation.effects: Prevents the target from fleeing and inflicts damage for 2-5 turns.
infestation.name: Infestation

poweruppunch.effects: Raises the user's Attack by one stage after inflicting damage.
poweruppunch.name: Power-Up Punch

oblivionwing.effects: Drains 75% of the damage inflicted to heal the user.
oblivionwing.name: Oblivion Wing

thousandarrows.effects: Grounds the target, and hits even Flying-type or levitating Pokémon.
thousandarrows.name: Thousand Arrows

thousandwaves.effects: Prevents the target from leaving battle.
thousandwaves.name: Thousand Waves

landswrath.effects: Inflicts regular damage with no additional effect.
landswrath.name: Land’s Wrath

lightofruin.effects: User receives 1/2 the damage inflicted in recoil.
lightofruin.name: Light of Ruin

originpulse.effects: Inflicts regular damage with no additional effect.
originpulse.name: Origin Pulse

precipiceblades.effects: Inflicts regular damage with no additional effect.
precipiceblades.name: Precipice Blades

dragonascent.effects: Lowers the user's Defense and Special Defense by one stage after inflicting damage.
dragonascent.name: Dragon Ascent
